</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d063n1-ptr" id="PJA11d063n1">1</a>

   <p>Engelbert Franois van Berckel, Pensionary of Amsterdam.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA11d063n2-ptr" id="PJA11d063n2">2</a>

   <p>Shakespeare, <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">Julius Caesar</span>, Act IV, scene iii, lines 218219. There the second line reads which, taken at the flood, leads on to fortune.</p>

